            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-6">Why Choose Us?</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-center text-content-active pl-4 relative">
                  <span class="absolute left-0 w-2 h-2 bg-spotlight rounded-full"></span>
                  15+ years of experience
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center text-content-active pl-4 relative">
